@node Reqs "Requirements"

                     WHAT DOES IT NEED TO RUN?
                     =========================

This demonstrations requires the following equipment:

One AMIGA ( Ohh, really :) ) equipped with the AGA chipset and a
68020 CPU or better. A harddrive or similar device are also required.
If you only have 2mb chip and no fastram, there may occur memory
problems, but then try to boot without startup-sequence..
Also plain A1200 owners may have some small timing problems. I am
sorry for this.. 


