@node Comms "Final Comments"

A word from the coder...
-------------------------

After many hours of modelling/rendering and coding, it has finally 
been completed. After several headaches, several cans of Coke &
sleepless nights... It's here..

It feels quite good..

We really would have liked doing this little demonstration in a
better resolution (the current one is based on 4x3 pixelblocks).
But, as the organisers of the Icing '96 party decided that the
demo had to work on 2mb chip only, this was not an option..

Pst! This whole demo contains 736(!) anim frames.. If we should
have used fullscreen you should have needed about 35MEG (!!!!)
hd space (lame 5mb limitations, eh? :) .



                                Sign. oRBIT / gIANTS


